<HEADLINE> Dallas 2, Chicago 1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DALLAS (AP) -- Forward Ariel Graziani scored Dallas' first goal  
then assisted on the game-winner Saturday as the Burn beat the 
Chicago Fire 2-1 in the opening game of the best-of-3 MLS Western 
Conference semifinals. 
</P>
