<HEADLINE> Timberwolves' Garrett Out 3-5 Weeks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MINNEAPOLIS (AP) -- Minnesota Timberwolves center Dean Garrett  
will be out three to five weeks after knee surgery. 
