season, will be the backup. 
</P>
<P>
	Saunders said he expects forward Tom Hammonds to miss three to  
five weeks with sore and swollen ankles from stress reactions in 
his heels. Sam Mitchell (knee) and Joe Smith (left foot) are also 
banged up. 
</P>
<P>
	``You'll see some funky lineups over the next three weeks,  
that's for sure,'' Saunders said. 
  	   	
